## Examples

Input: "I go north"
Output: `{"action_type": "move", "target": "exit_north", "detail": "Player heads north through the doorway", "follow_up": null, "soft_state_patches": []}`

Input: "I search the room thoroughly"
Output: `{"action_type": "examine", "target": "room_entrance", "rigorous": true, "detail": "Player conducts a thorough search of the entrance hall", "follow_up": null, "soft_state_patches": []}`

Input: "I pick up the rusty key and unlock the padlock"
